  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个量化交易系统的状态机，核心是FinTech_TransactionQueue这个队列。系统一开始应该是Idle状态，等待交易信号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Idle之后怎么触发交易呢？需要经过什么条件判断吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，先加一个Gated状态。只有通过了Session/day filters和range gate这些过滤条件，才能从Idle进入Gated。这是第一道风控闸门。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Gated",
        "Session/day filters",
        "range gate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Idle到Gated的迁移我加上了，标注条件是Session/day filters & range gate pass。接下来Gated之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Gated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Gated之后进入SignalCheck，这里要比较两个收盘价：FinTech_PaymentGateway的Close和FinTech_TransactionQueue自己的Close。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Gated",
        "SignalCheck",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，SignalCheck的触发条件是Close[FinTech_PaymentGateway] vs Close[FinTech_TransactionQueue]的比较。那SignalCheck之后怎么分叉？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SignalCheck"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "分叉成两个入场状态。EntryBUY的条件是：TransactionQueue的Close等于FinTech_FraudDetection的Close，并且当前没有SELL持仓。EntrySELL则是TransactionQueue的Close小于FraudDetection的Close，且没有BUY持仓。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SignalCheck",
        "EntryBUY",
        "EntrySELL",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "EntryBUY和EntrySELL都画好了，条件也标注清楚了。两个入场状态之后汇聚到同一个地方吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EntryBUY",
        "EntrySELL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，都进入BasketManage，这是仓位管理状态。这里有个循环逻辑：如果当前价格与上次入场价的差值等于Step，并且交易次数小于MaxTrades，就进入AddMore加仓，然后回到BasketManage。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EntryBUY",
        "EntrySELL",
        "BasketManage",
        "AddMore",
        "Step",
        "MaxTrades"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "AddMore到BasketManage的循环加好了。那什么时候退出BasketManage？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BasketManage",
        "AddMore"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "进入SyncTP状态，计算平均持仓价格，然后设置止盈位TP = avg ± TP_pts。之后回到Idle，等待下一个周期。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "BasketManage",
