      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "SyncTP到Idle的回流完成了。不过Idle状态还需要几条异常退出路径吧？比如风控止损？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SyncTP",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，三条退出路径。EquityStop是浮动盈亏小于0且亏损绝对值触及阈值；HiddenTP是隐性止盈 basket profit 达到目标；DailyTarget是启用了日目标且当日收益已达Daily_Target。这三条都先到Flat状态平仓。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "EquityStop",
