      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "整个状态机闭环完成了。我检查一下：Idle是中心枢纽，有进有出；Gated和SignalCheck是前置过滤；EntryBUY/EntrySELL互斥入场；BasketManage和AddMore形成加仓循环；SyncTP计算均价设止盈；三条风控线EquityStop、HiddenTP、DailyTarget都汇聚到Flat再回Idle。结构清晰。",
